title: PMS 2.0 597 - LIVE From Radio Row In LA, Aidan Hutchinson, Kurt Warner, Seth Rollins, Chuck Pagano, Carson Palmer, & AJ Hawk
description: On today's show, Pat, AJ Hawk, and the boys are live from Radio Row in LA and have an absolutely loaded show with potential #1 pick in the NFL Draft Aidan Hutchinson, Hall of Famer Kurt Warner, WWE Superstar Seth Rollins, Coach Chuck Pagano, and former Cincinnati Bengals legend, Carson Palmer. Make sure you subscribe to youtube.com/thepatmcafeeshow and listen every day on Mad Dog Radio, Sirius XM Channel 82. We appreciate you all for listening, come and laugh with us, cheers.
